&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.greenhouse.com/mission&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;mission&lt;/a&gt; at Greenhouse is to make every company great at hiring – so we go to great lengths to hire great people because we believe that they’re the foundation of our success. At Greenhouse, you’ll join a team that collaborates purposefully, fosters inclusivity, and communicates with transparency and accountability so we can help companies measurably improve the way they hire.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us to do the best work of your career, solving meaningful problems with remarkable teams.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Greenhouse is looking for a seasoned&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Upper &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mid-Market Account Executive&lt;/strong&gt; to join our Sales team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a vital part of our Revenue team, you&#39;ll play a crucial role in driving Greenhouse&#39;s growth strategy and helping the company meet its goals. In this senior individual contributor position, your main focus will be securing new clients within a strategic segment of our business. You&#39;ll manage the entire sales process, from generating leads to closing deals, contributing to the growth of our already impressive customer base of over 7,000 companies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who will love this job&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An evangelist – &lt;/strong&gt;you believe in our product and are excited to tell our story with authenticity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A bold salesperson – &lt;/strong&gt;you&#39;re confident in your ability to win deals and advise customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A high-performer – &lt;/strong&gt;you love to sell, and you have the track record that shows you’re good at it&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A consultant – &lt;/strong&gt;you can navigate difficult conversations to help customers understand value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A positive influence – &lt;/strong&gt;you’re positive in the face of adversity and love the challenge of a constantly evolving environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be an impactful, experienced player on a high-­performing sales team&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effectively guide prospects through a thoughtful, value-oriented sales process to hit (and exceed!) your quarterly goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively prospect to supplement the lead flow provided by a dedicated team of Sales Development Representatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively manage your pipeline of opportunities to deliver timely, accurate forecasts and ensure clear visibility into revenue performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel occasionally to on-site client meetings, industry events and conferences, internal sales kick-offs, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Additional projects and responsibilities as business needs require&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You should have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated senior level experience with full-cycle sales with a track record of multi-year success generating pipeline and exceeding $1M+ quotas&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to communicate, present and influence key stakeholders at all levels of an organization, including executive and C-level&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong business acumen, with the ability to build compelling business cases for strategic technology investments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in HR Tech industry, a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your own unique talents – Your background has given you a unique perspective and set of transferable skills that aren&#39;t always in alignment with a given role - but those are qualities we value at Greenhouse. If you don&#39;t meet 100% of the qualifications outlined above, we still strongly encourage you to apply&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
