&lt;p&gt;Join us to do the best work of your career, solving meaningful problems with remarkable teams.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Mid-Market Account Manager &lt;/strong&gt;for our Account Management team here at Greenhouse!&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Our Account Management team drives customer retention, growth and expansion opportunities, as well as continued product optimization and adoption. As an Account Manager, you will own the renewals and up-selling of new products into our rapidly growing ecosystem of customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will not only ensure a premium experience for our customers by understanding their business objectives, but also partner with our Customer Success, Marketing, Product and Finance teams to streamline workflows and communication processes within Greenhouse.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who will love this job&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;strategic hunter&lt;/strong&gt; – you thrive in a competitive environment and can clearly see the full picture of an account, driving revenue by recommending the best solution for both Greenhouse and our customers&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A&lt;strong&gt; thoughtful mediator&lt;/strong&gt; – you&#39;re successful, effective, and helpful through tough situations and hard-to-close negotiations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;collaborative teammate&lt;/strong&gt; – you enjoy working with others and utilizing strong partnerships to achieve the best outcome, whether internal or external&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;hardworking problem solver –&lt;/strong&gt; you&#39;re not afraid to test, iterate, and chip in ideas when it comes to solutions. You roll with the punches and can adapt, but are excited to be a part of the fix&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and put together strategic account plans that map out expansion and other upsell opportunities as part of the broader sales organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain an active pipeline of forecasted renewals and expansions to meet quota objectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Customer Success Managers for shared management of your customer relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Position yourself as a strategic partner to key stakeholders and champions within named accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continued assessment of Greenhouse’s alignment with customer’s business objectives and goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and mitigate churn risk clearly and own resolution strategies, advising sales leadership of ideal resolutions wherever appropriate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be an active participant in building and improving internal operational processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Additional projects and responsibilities as business needs require&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You should have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3 years experience in a relevant mid-market quota carrying role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quota-carrying experience (e.g., Renewals, Sales, Account Management), preferably in a SaaS organization, with demonstrated success in generating expansion pipeline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing fast paced strategic commercial sales processes for MID-market+ companies (500 person + organisations)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent time, prioritisation, organisation, and process management skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong pipeline management and familiarity with sales-oriented CRM tools&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven success navigating organisations and ability to quickly identify the decision-makers and the decision-making process for SaaS investments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to craft narratives and prove customer value through comprehensive business reviews and strategic touch-points&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional verbal, written, and presentation skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your own unique talents! If you don’t meet 100% of the qualifications outlined above, tell us why you’d be a great fit for this role in your cover letter&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
